    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>tofu</strong>, and cut the block into 2 pieces per person</p><p>Pat the <strong>tofu pieces </strong>dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Season the <strong>tofu</strong> <strong>pieces </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and sprinkle both sides with <strong>flour</strong> until fully coated, then tap off any excess</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1629284768779-x200.jpg",
