            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person and set aside for garnish</p><p>Add your <strong>blanched peas</strong> to the reserved pot, cover them with<strong> boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 1 min or until they're warmed through, then drain and return to the pot with a knob of<strong> butter</strong></p><p>Mash the <strong>peas</strong> until they come together nicely – these are your <strong>mushy peas</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
