      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>battered tofu </strong>with the <strong>chunky chips</strong> and <strong>mushy peas </strong>to the side</p><p>Sprinkle the chips with the<strong> remaining red wine vinegar </strong>– these are your <strong>salt & vinegar chips</strong></p><p>Serve with your <strong>ketchup</strong> and <strong>lemon mayo</strong> to the side for dipping, and garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
